%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20LIVE%3A%20Sensex%20slumps%201%2C870%20pts%2C%20Nifty%20opens%20below%2024%2C000%20as%20Brent%20rise%20on%20US-Iran%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773027993000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-09%2F10%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1757479033-9917.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-march-9-nse-bse-sensex-today-nifty-gift-nifty-oil-price-us-israel-iran-tension-ipo-share-market-today-126030900103_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sensex%20Today%20%7C%20Stock%20Market%20LIVE%20Updates%2C%20Monday%3A%20The%20Nifty50%20and%20the%20Sensex%20fell%20sharply%20at%20open%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-march-9-nse-bse-sensex-today-nifty-gift-nifty-oil-price-us-israel-iran-tension-ipo-share-market-today-126030900103_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-march-9-nse-bse-sensex-today-nifty-gift-nifty-oil-price-us-israel-iran-tension-ipo-share-market-today-126030900103_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-march-9-nse-bse-sensex-today-nifty-gift-nifty-oil-price-us-israel-iran-tension-ipo-share-market-today-126030900103_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oil%20surges%20above%20the%20dreaded%20%24100%20level%20as%20Iran-war%20market%20disruption%20deepens%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shehran%20oil%20depot%2C%20in%20Tehran%2C%20Iran%20on%20March%208%2C%202026%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ae0b46d3e2f1aef36a33c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOil%20jumped%20above%20%24100%20per%20barrel%20in%20Sunday%20trading.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20price%20of%20crude%20oil%20spiked%20above%20%24100%20per%20barrel%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20more%20than%20three%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Iran%20war%20continues%20to%20affect%20crude%20supply%20from%20the%20region%20and%20cripple%20global%20oil%20flows.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWall%20Street%20strategists%20have%20warned%20that%20a%20prolonged%20breach%20of%20%24100%20could%20damage%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20hitting%20%24100%20per%20barrel%20was%20increasingly%20being%20bandied%20about%20as%20a%20possibility%20after%20the%20Iran%20war%20started.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20supposed%20to%20happen%20this%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20futures%20spiked%20above%20%24100%20per%20barrel%20when%20trading%20kicked%20off%20on%20Sunday%20evening%20and%20continued%20surging%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBrent%20crude%20oil%20futures%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWTI%20crude%3C%2Fa%3E%20gaining%20about%2030%25%20to%20nearly%20%24120%20per%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20was%20trading%20around%20%24114%20a%20barrel%20at%2011%3A13%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20while%20WTI%20was%20around%20%24113%20a%20barrel.%20Prices%20of%20both%20grades%20have%20nearly%20doubled%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Iran%20war%2C%20the%20%24100-per-barrel%20level%20has%20been%20viewed%20as%20a%20psychologically%20significant%20threshold%20that%2C%20when%20crossed%2C%20would%20spell%20inflationary%20trouble%20for%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-gas-prices-climb-highest-trumps-term-oil-iran-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egas%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20pump%20just%20rose%20to%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20Trump's%20second%20term%2C%20and%20that%20stocks%20are%20coming%20off%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-february-jobs-report-oil-prices-economy-iran-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroughest%20week%20in%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20both%20pieces%20of%20that%20equation%20appear%20to%20be%20moving%20into%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fj2GPG%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fj2GPG%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20narrative%20is%20the%20same%20one%20that%20sent%20crude%20prices%20nearly%2030%25%20higher%20last%20week%3A%20as%20long%20as%20the%20Iran%20war%20rages%20on%20%E2%80%94%20and%20as%20long%20as%20countries%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20continue%20to%20cut%20production%20%E2%80%94%20prices%20will%20move%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20focal%20point%20has%20been%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20which%20handles%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20world's%20oil%20flow.%20As%20regional%20disruption%20has%20persisted%2C%20the%20scope%20of%20concerns%20has%20expanded%20to%20the%20entire%20global%20oil%20logistics%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20oil%20shock%20won't%20end%20until%20ships%20can%20sail%20freely%20through%20the%20Strait%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20veteran%20strategist%20Ed%20Yardeni.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20then%2C%20the%20financial%20markets%20are%20likely%20to%20become%20increasingly%20concerned%20about%20a%201970s-style%20stagflation%20scenario%3B%20back%20then%2C%20the%20period%20of%20stagflation%20included%20two%20recessions%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWarren%20Patterson%2C%20the%20head%20of%20commodities%20strategy%20at%20ING%2C%20wrote%20that%20even%20if%20shipments%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20restart%2C%20producers%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20quickly%20restore%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20production%20offline%20and%20no%20clear%20signs%20that%20the%20conflict%20is%20easing%2C%20traders%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20factor%20in%20the%20risk%20of%20an%20extended%20disruption%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%2C%20as%20long%20as%20we%20don't%20see%20oil%20moving%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20oil%20prices%20will%20only%20move%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20Patterson%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJos%C3%A9%20Torres%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20Interactive%20Brokers%2C%20told%20BI%20last%20week%20that%20%24100%20would%20mark%20a%20true%20price%20shock%20for%20oil%2C%20leading%20to%20persistently%20high%20inflation%20and%20a%20possible%20down%20year%20for%20stocks.%20(The%20equity%20market%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-dow-oil-prices-inflation-shock-us-iran-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20feeling%20that%20pressure%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20CIO%20Mike%20Wilson%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20most%20bullish%20stock%20strategists%20on%20Wall%20Street%20%E2%80%94%20has%20also%20been%20eyeing%20%24100%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-stock-market-impact-brent-forecast-mike-wilson-wti-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20level%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20he'd%20lower%20his%20base-case%20scenario%20for%20stocks%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20oil%20keeps%20rising%2C%20market%20pros%20have%20said%20to%20expect%20more%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%24120%20for%20Brent%2C%20you're%20at%20zero%20growth.%20That's%20the%20trigger%20for%20a%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20Bruce%20Richards%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Marathon%20Asset%20Management%2C%20said%20last%20week.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20I%20believe.%20And%20I%20believe%20that's%20what%20the%20markets%20believe%2C%20although%20no%20one%20said%20it%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c9f98bc-3487-43fe-b03d-0fb12631a218%5C%22%3EThe%20spillover%3A%20dollar%20gains%20and%20stocks%20slump%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prospects%20of%20an%20oil%20price%20shock%20and%20its%20fallout%20on%20global%20economic%20growth%20spread%20through%20the%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20the%20greenback%20jumped%20to%20a%20three-month%20high%20against%20the%20euro%20and%20gained%20as%20much%20as%200.4%25%20against%20the%20Japanese%20yen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Dollar%20Index%20was%200.6%25%20higher%20as%20of%2011%3A14%20p.m.%20ET.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stronger%20dollar%20weighed%20on%20dollar-denominated%20commodities%2C%20even%20the%20haven%20trade%20in%20gold.%20The%20spot%20gold%20price%20was%201.5%25%20lower%20at%20%245%2C093%20per%20troy%20ounce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20main%20US%20stock%20market%20futures%20were%20about%202%25%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStock%20markets%20in%20Asia%20started%20the%20week%20deep%20in%20the%20red%2C%20with%20Japan's%20Nikkei%20225%20losing%20over%207%25%20and%20South%20Korea's%20Kospi%20slumping%20by%20over%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHong%20Kong's%20Hang%20Seng%20was%20down%20about%203%25%20and%20Taiwan's%20Taiex%20lost%20over%206%25.%20Australia's%20ASX200%20dropped%20over%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsia%20is%20a%20major%20energy%20importer%20and%20is%20especially%20exposed%20to%20the%20disruption%20in%20oil%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20take%20months%20for%20energy%20flows%20in%20Asia%20to%20normalize%2C%20wrote%20June%20Goh%2C%20a%20senior%20oil%20market%20analyst%20at%20data%20provider%20Sparta%20Commodities%2C%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B10%20days%20of%20Straits%20of%20Hormuz%20disruption%20%3D%20at%20least%2060%20days%20of%20pain%20to%20the%20energy%20flow%20in%20Asia.%20And%20I%20am%20being%20optimistic%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Goh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-shock-brent-wti-crude-100-threshold-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773027550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ae0b53fd4fbd083f29bc62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-shock-brent-wti-crude-100-threshold-iran-war-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Iran%20war%20has%20forced%20oil%20producers%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20to%20cut%20supply%2C%20putting%20further%20upward%20pressure%20on%20crude%20prices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jciolli%40businessinsider.com%20(Joe%20Ciolli%2CHuileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-shock-brent-wti-crude-100-threshold-iran-war-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata's%20in-house%20feud%20is%20going%20public.%20What's%20stopping%20its%20equity%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773027119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-03%2F09%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1773025694-139.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-s-in-house-feud-is-going-public-what-s-stopping-its-equity-126030900136_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trust%20dominance%20and%20a%20history%20of%20family%20feuds%20test%20Tata's%20ownership%20structure%20as%20pressure%20grows%20to%20list%20the%20holding%20company%20as%20regulatory%20and%20governance%20pressures%20mount%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww