024.%20I've%20taught%20many%20engineers%20and%20customers%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20semi-retirement%20mode%20now.%20Technology%20isn't%20work%20to%20me%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20ChatGPT%20came%20out%2C%20I%20jumped%20on%20it.%20About%20six%20or%20eight%20months%20ago%2C%20when%20vibe%20coding%20became%20hot%2C%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I%20need%20to%20try%20this%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20researched%20and%20found%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femergent-vibe-coding-funding-khosla-softbank-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEmergent%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20I%20liked%20is%20that%20they%20had%20the%20full%20stack.%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20connect%20anything%20or%20get%20my%20developers%20on%20the%20line%20to%20handle%20the%20back-end.%20I%20could%20just%20get%20on%20there%20and%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20began%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20simple%20things.%20Now%20I've%20probably%20done%20a%20dozen%20or%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineers-on-vibe-coding-ai-tools-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evibe-coded%20apps.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20two%20were%20for%20this%20AED%20company.%20They%20wanted%20the%20ability%20to%20access%20their%20existing%20camera%20provider's%20website%20and%20extract%20their%20data.%20So%20I%20vibe-coded%20an%20app%20that%20would%20do%20that%20%E2%80%94%20pull%20that%20data%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20vibe-coded%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-ceo-vibe-coding-software-replace-apps-mustafa-suleyman-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20voice%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20them.%20It's%20a%20web%20app%2C%20so%20you%20go%20to%20it%20on%20your%20phone%2C%20hit%20a%20button%2C%20and%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20our%20AED%20status%3F%26quot%3B%20It%20checks%20the%20database%2C%20then%20returns%20the%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20showed%20the%20CEO%20a%20demo%2C%20he%20lit%20up.%20He%20thought%20it%20was%20the%20coolest%20thing%20he'd%20ever%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3378625-71e7-4312-9b7f-56a531164e5a%5C%22%3EOlder%20people%20can%20move%20fast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20think%20an%20old%20guy%20like%20me%20would%20have%20a%20flip%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20as%20a%20ham%20radio%20operator%20at%2013%2C%20I%20was%20using%20Morse%20code%20on%20tubes%2C%20transmitters%2C%20and%20receivers.%20To%20go%20from%20that%20to%20what%20we've%20gone%20through%20with%20phones%20and%20cellphones%2C%20and%20then%20to%20watch%20that%20transition%20over%20the%20years%20into%20AI%20and%20be%20closely%20involved%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20just%20love%20the%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20both%20the%20hardware%20and%20the%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20young%20kids%20today%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagentic-engineering-andrej-karpathy-vibe-coding-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einto%20software%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebut%20don't%20know%20much%20about%20the%20hardware%20piece.%20Having%20a%20wide%20background%20comes%20in%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20often%20an%20assumption%20that%20gray%20hair%20means%20outdated%20technology%20skills.%20I%20understand%20where%20that%20perception%20comes%20from%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20always%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20us%20have%20moved%20just%20as%20quickly%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20AI%20as%20younger%20professionals.%20The%20advantage%20we%20bring%20is%20perspective%3A%20decades%20of%20experience%20that%20allow%20us%20to%20apply%20AI%20strategically%2C%20not%20just%20technically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20would%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-ai-chatbot-replacing-jobs-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eolder%20people%20retire%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20lose%20purpose.%20I've%20never%20had%20that%20problem%20because%20I've%20always%20had%20a%20passion%20for%20doing%20technical%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20constantly%20on%20my%20laptop%20and%20phone%2C%20doing%20something%20related%20to%20AI%20and%20learning.%20You've%20got%20to%20watch%20a%20lot%20of%20YouTube%20and%20social%20media%2C%20learn%20what's%20coming%20and%20what's%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c40c6798-d6a8-403a-a798-a7c997255029%5C%22%3EHow%20seniors%20can%20use%20AI%20for%20everyday%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20teaching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-over-age-80-embrace-ai-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20seniors%3C%2Fa%3E%20now.%20In%20my%20class%20back%20in%20November%2C%20we%20were%20talking%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-advisor-peter-navarro-ai-internalize-data-center-costs-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20what's%20behind%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lady%20named%20Sue%20who's%20100%20years%20old.%20Near%20the%20end%20of%20the%20class%2C%20Sue%20came%20up%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20a%20semiconductor%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20hardware%20background%2C%20so%20I%20answered%20her%20question%20at%20a%20very%20high%20level.%20She%20listened%20intently%20and%20wrote%20down%20a%20few%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20class%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20need%20to%20do%20more%20for%20her.%26quot%3B%20So%20I%20used%20AI%20to%20create%20a%20video%20that%20went%20through%20the%20evolution%20of%20tubes%20in%20the%2020s%20and%2030s%20%E2%80%94%20things%20they%20could%20relate%20to%20%E2%80%94%20and%20old%20radios%20and%20TVs.%20Then%20we%20went%20to%20transistors%20in%20the%20late%2040s%20and%2050s%2C%20and%20what%20that%20meant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seniors%20I%20taught%20have%20now%20learned%20enough%20to%20take%20over%20their%20internal%20resident%20newsletter%20and%20use%20AI%20to%20help%20write%20it.%20They%20also%20created%20images%20for%20the%20newsletter%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnon-technical-people-vibecoding-lessons-ai-apps-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20shop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20check%20for%20bargains%2C%20and%20research%20their%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20shown%20them%20how%20to%20recognize%20different%20plants%20and%20birds%20with%20AI.%20They'll%20walk%20through%20their%20garden%20area%2C%20take%20a%20picture%2C%20and%20ask%20ChatGPT%20or%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20vibe%20coding%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acmlee%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ecmlee%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-vibe-coding-seniors-ai-lewis-dickson-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773014402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698d95bde1ba468a96abea5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-vibe-coding-seniors-ai-lewis-dickson-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%2078%2C%20he's%20vibe%20coding%20and%20teaching%20AI%20to%20seniors.%20Retirement%20hasn't%20slowed%20his%20passion%20for%20technology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmlee%40insider.com%20(Lee%20Chong%20Ming)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-vibe-coding-seniors-ai-lewis-dickson-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2280K%20watch%20live%20as%20YouTuber%20Anurag%20Dobhal%20crashes%20SUV%20into%20DME%20divider%3B%20critical%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773014221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%