ider.com%2F698f4ee4d3c7faef0ece3e69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOil%20prices%20look%20like%20they're%20edging%20closer%20to%20a%20key%20threshold%20that%20suggests%20inflation%20could%20start%20to%20rise%20and%20economic%20growth%20could%20get%20hit%20from%20the%20war%20on%20Iran%2C%20market%20pros%20say.%3Cp%3EPavel%20Mikheyev%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOil%20prices%20surpassed%20%24100%20a%20barrel%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20energy%20secretary%20is%20working%20to%20reassure%20Americans%20that%20high%20gas%20prices%20won't%20last.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChris%20Wright%20said%20the%20conflict%20in%20Iran%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20a%20%26quot%3Blong-term%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Energy%20Secretary%20Chris%20Wright%20made%20the%20morning%20show%20rounds%20on%20Sunday%20to%20downplay%20concerns%20about%20surging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-gas-prices-climb-highest-trumps-term-oil-iran-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egas%20and%20oil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20assuring%20Americans%20that%20the%20war%20with%20Iran%20isn't%20%26quot%3Blong-term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20the%20price%20of%20a%20barrel%20of%20oil%20surged%20passed%20%24100%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20almost%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20you%20are%20seeing%20is%20emotional%20reactions%20and%20fear%20that%20this%20is%20a%20long-term%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20told%20%26quot%3BFace%20the%20Nation%26quot%3B%20on%20CBS%20News.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20long-term%20war.%20This%20is%20a%20temporary%20movement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWright%20made%20similar%20remarks%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Fox%20News%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20run-up%20on%20prices%20doesn't%20have%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20any%20shortage%20of%20barrels%20of%20oil%20or%20natural%20gas.%20It's%20just%20fear%20and%20perception%2C%20the%20unknown%20that%20this%20could%20be%20some%20long%2C%20drawn-out%20crisis%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-weapons-used-to-attack-iran-fend-off-retaliation-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eairstrikes%20on%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%2028%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20moved%20quickly%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20a%20narrow%20waterway%20critical%20to%20the%20movement%20of%20oil%20around%20the%20world.%20About%2020%25%20of%20the%20globe's%20petroleum%20liquids%20pass%20through%20the%20Strait.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20are%20storage%20tanks%20across%20the%20Gulf%2C%20they%20are%20already%20nearing%20capacity%20after%20a%20week%20of%20conflict%20and%20limited%20shipping%20options%2C%20forcing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-iran-strait-hormuz-disruption-storage-crude-output-risk-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducers%20to%20reduce%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Iraq's%20oil%20output%20has%20shrunk%20by%2060%25%20since%20last%20week%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%20Other%20countries%2C%20like%20Kuwait%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20have%20also%20reduced%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20means%20higher%20gas%20prices%20for%20Americans.%20The%20US%20Energy%20Information%20Administration%20says%20gas%20prices%20averaged%20%242.93%20on%20February%2023.%20By%20March%202%2C%20they%20were%20at%20%243.15.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20they%20were%20%243.40.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20media%20tour%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Wright%20said%20regular%20ship%20traffic%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hurmoz%20could%20resume%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20few%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20gas%20prices%20could%20ease%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20it%20back%20below%20%243%20a%20gallon%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20again%20before%20too%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20told%20CNN's%20%26quot%3BState%20of%20the%20Union.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BYou%20never%20know%20exactly%20the%20timeframe%20of%20this%2C%20but%2C%20in%20the%20worst%20case%2C%20this%20is%20a%20weeks%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20months%2C%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-oil-iran-energy-chris-wright-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773012923000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ad9e33fd4fbd083f29bb75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-oil-iran-energy-chris-wright-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Energy%20Secretary%20Chris%20Wright%20blamed%20%26quot%3Bemotional%20reactions%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20surge%20in%20gas%20prices%20and%20said%20they%20should%20return%20to%20normal%20in%20weeks%2C%20not%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-oil-iran-energy-chris-wright-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Even%20I%20was%20doubting%20myself'%3A%20Abhishek%20thanks%20SKY%2C%20Gambhir%20after%20match-winning%20knock%20in%20final%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773012600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129284220%2Cimgsize-42664.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Feven-i-was-doubting-myself-abhishek-sharma-thanks-suryakumar-yadav-coach-gautam-gambhir-after-match-winning-knock-in-final%2Farticleshow%2F129284075.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abhishek%20made%20an%20impact%20in%20the%20final%20against