y%22%3A%22Two%20persons%20accused%20of%20killing%20Osman%20Hadi%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20special%20task%20force%20(STF)%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20police%2C%20an%20official%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-accused-in-bangladesh-leader-osman-hadis-murder-arrested-by-bengal-police-11187069%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20polyamorous%20and%20my%202%20partners%20and%20I%20live%20with%20our%20kids.%20Here's%20how%20we%20navigate%20coparenting%20together.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225068%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20people%20are%20cooking%20the%20same%20dish%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69613be464858d02d218131d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223379%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20shares%20coparenting%20duties%20with%20her%20two%20partners.%20%3Cp%3EDGLimages%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20met%20Nick%20in%202018%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20together%20ever%20since.%20We%20welcomed%20our%20first%20child%20in%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202022%2C%20I%20felt%20something%20was%20missing%2C%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20open%20up%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20our%20family%20has%20two%20children%20and%20three%20parents.%20We%20work%20hard%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20coparent%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20relationship%20between%20you%20guys%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20two%20brothers%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20that%20your%20ex%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20just%20a%20few%20of%20the%20questions%20my%20family%20might%20get%20whenever%20someone%20tries%20to%20figure%20out%20exactly%20what's%20going%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-uses-my-home-parenting-time-saved-our-co-parenting-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20our%20household.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20I've%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-polyamorous-people-want-you-to-know-about-what-its-really-like-to-have-multiple-partners-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etwo%20romantic%20partners%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fa%3E%20During%20that%20time%2C%20we've%20navigated%20toddlerhood%2C%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20now%20life%20with%20two%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20all%20under%20one%20roof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20often%20nervous%20to%20ask%20questions%20when%20they%20first%20hear%20about%20our%20situation.%20But%20I%20always%20say%20I'll%20answer%20anything%20asked%20with%20genuine%20curiosity.%20I%20know%20our%20life%20isn't%20typical%2C%20and%20most%20people%20have%20never%20met%20a%20woman%20with%20two%20male%20partners%20outside%20the%20pages%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fromance-book-recommendations-for-emily-henry-fans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espicy%20romance%20novel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20works%20best%20for%20our%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a80da05-070e-4fe1-bf77-43e454224cb5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20went%20from%20a%20traditional%20relationship%20to%20a%20polyamorous%20household%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20met%20Nick%20in%20college%20in%202018%2C%20and%20we%20have%20been%20together%20ever%20since.%20The%20two%20of%20us%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-boston-for-san-francisco-to-live-near-grown-children-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20across%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20(and%20back)%2C%20gone%20through%20a%20miscarriage%2C%20job%20loss%2C%20and%20in%202021%2C%20we%20welcomed%20our%20first%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20by%20late%202022%2C%20something%20felt%20off%20for%20me.%20I%20loved%20our%20life%20together%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20shake%20the%20feeling%20that%20something%20was%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20therapist's%20guidance%2C%20I%20started%20exploring%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-partner-is-monogamous-but-im-not-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eopen%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20took%20me%20months%20to%20bring%20the%20topic%20up%20to%20Nick%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20him%20to%20think%20I%20was%20unhappy%20or%20that%20he%20wasn't%20enough%20for%20me.%20To%20his%20credit%2C%20he%20met%20the%20idea%20with%20compassion%20and%20curiosity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20of%202023%2C%20I%20met%20Christian%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-app-costs-rise-matches-hidden-behind-paywalls-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edating%20app%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Right%20away%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20he%20was%20someone%20I%20wanted%20in%20my%20life%20and%20as%20part%20of%20my%20family.%20His%20openness%2C%20which%20I%20had%20struggled%20to%20find%20elsewhere%2C%20felt%20natural%20and%20easy%2C%20even%20though%20this%20experience%20was%20a%20first%20for%20him%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntegrating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fopen-relationship%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethird%20partner%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20especially%20with%20a%20child%2C%20took%20time%20and%20effort.%20There%20were%20lots%20of%20conversations%20and%20logistical%20adjustments%20that%20we%20had%20to%20navigate%20together.%20There%20were%20awkward%20discussions%20and%20emotional%20growing%20pains.%20How%20do%20we%20tell%20our%20families%20about%20this%3F%20How%20do%20we%20explain%20this%20to%20our%20then%202-year-old%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fjealousy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20we%20mitigate%20jealousy%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Where%20are%20we%20all%20going%20to%20sleep%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20baby%20conversation%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222592%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20poses%20with%20her%20family.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aae84dfd4fbd083f29a68e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222043%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20that%20though%20their%20situation%20may%20be%20unique%20to%20some%2C%20it%20works%20well%20for%20their%20family.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Victoria%20DeVita.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222164afc7-9997-4ef3-bd78-53607c69bbe8%5C%22%3EParenting%20as%20a%20team%20of%20three%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20Christian%20moved%20in%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20have%20a%20second%20baby%20was%20a%20big%20one%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20Nick%20and%20I%20wanted%20another%20child%2C%20but%20we%20also%20wanted%20to%20include%20Christian%20in%20the%20conversation.%20We%20talked%20through%20fears%2C%20hopes%2C%20and%20what%20this%20new%20chapter%20would%20mean%20for%20our%20family.%20It%20was%20a%20moment%20that%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20honest%2C%20intentional%2C%20and%20aligned%20as%20a%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Christian%20moved%20in%20a%20few%20months%20later%2C%20it%20required%20more%20adjustments.%20We%20moved%20into%20a%20three-bedroom%20apartment%20that%20could%20accommodate%20everyone%2C%20including%20my%20growing%20baby%20bump.%20We%20had%20to%20establish%20new%20routines%2C%20the%20aforementioned%20sleeping%20arrangements%2C%20and%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20integrate%20everyone%20into%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Christian%20came%20into%20our%20lives%2C%20our%20first%20child%20was%20only%202%2C%20so%20there%20wasn't%20too%20much%20we%20needed%20to%20explain%20to%20her.%20Now%20that%20she's%204%2C%20we've%20had%20more%20conversations%20about%20how%20Christian%20is%20her%20parent%2C%20just%20like%20mom%20and%20dad.%20She%20mostly%20calls%20him%20Christian%20or%20Tin%20Tin%2C%20but%20also%20acknowledges%20that%20he%20is%20her%20dad%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20last%20year%20has%20shown%20us%20that%20parenting%20together%20is%20our%20main%20focus%20and%20our%20strength.%20Details%20that%20used%20to%20send%20me%20into%20a%20logistical%20spiral%20now%20flow%20smoothly.%20Christian%20handles%20the%20morning%20routine%20for%20our%20now%204-year-old%2C%20while%20Nick%20takes%20charge%20at%20bedtime.%20We%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivorce-bought-house-with-ex-duplex-co-parenting-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshare%20responsibility%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20baby%20during%20the%20day%2C%20stepping%20in%20wherever%20needed.%20School%20drop-off%20and%20pickup%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20day%2C%20and%20we%20coordinate%20those%20days%20carefully%20so%20nothing%20falls%20through%20the%20cracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20make%20a%20point%20to%20present%20a%20united%20front.%20If%20one%20parent%20says%20no%2C%20the%20others%20honor%20that%20decision%20(although%20our%20daughter%20has%20definitely%20taken%20advantage%20of%20the%20moments%20when%20we%20haven't%20compared%20notes%20yet).%20We%20all%20attend%20as%20many%20events%20as%20possible%2C%20including%20doctors'%20appointments%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-you-need-to-ask-at-parent-teacher-conference-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eparent-teacher%20conferences%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20birthday%20parties.%20Sometimes%20we%20rotate%2C%20sometimes%20we%20all%20go%2C%20but%20the%20message%20is%20clear%3A%20every%20parent%20is%20committed%20and%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20teamwork%20makes%20life%20smoother%20and%20enables%20us%20to%20support%20one%20another%20emotionally.%20When%20one%20of%20us%20is%20exhausted%2C%20the%20others%20step%20in%20without%20hesitation.%20I%20believe%20the%20kids%20benefit%20from%20multiple%20perspectives%2C%20consistent%20attention%2C%20and%20a%20household%20where%20collaboration%20is%20consistently%20modeled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df4b1732-feda-4fc5-98cd-287f0555881e%5C%22%3EOur%20life%20works%20well%20for%20us%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20often%20assume%20polyamory%20is%20about%20romance%20or%20novelty%2C%20but%20for%20us%2C%20it%20has%20become%20about%20parenting%2C%20teamwork%2C%20and%20intentional%20communication.%20Our%20children%20are%20loved%2C%20supported%2C%20and%20surrounded%20by%20adults%20who%20show%20up%20for%20them%20and%20for%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20oldest%20daughter%20does%20not%20question%20why%20she%20has%20three%20parents.%20To%20her%2C%20this%20is%20normal.%20When%20she%20draws%20family%20portraits%2C%20all%20three%20of%20us%20are%20always%20included%2C%20hand%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20that%20is%20what%20family%20looks%20like.%20Not%20defined%20by%20tradition%2C%20but%20by%20love%2C%20presence%2C%20and%20shared%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-polyamorous-family-coparents-kids-work-together-teamwork-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772992681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69613c0864858d02d2181327%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-polyamorous-family-coparents-kids-work-together-teamwork-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20know%20our%20life%20isn't%20typical%2C%20but%20it%20works%20well%20for%20our%20family.%20I'm%20happy%20that%20our%20kids%20have%20three%20parents%20who%20care%20for%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Victoria%20DeVita)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-polyamorous-family-coparents-kids-work-together-teamwork-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Country%20Joe%20McDonald%2C%20Woodstock%2