l%20of%20vintage%20clothes%2C%20which%20I%20now%20sell%20online.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scottlynn%20Krause%20posing%20with%20her%20mom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a1cd921fb3fcb426489a83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScottlynn%20Krause%20and%20her%20mom%20created%20an%20online%20store%20to%20sell%20vintage%201980s%20items%20they%20inherited.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Scottlynn%20Krause%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EScottlynn%20Krause%20and%20her%20mother%20created%20CS80%20Vintage%2C%20an%20online%20vintage%20store%20based%20in%20Sacramento.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20inherited%20a%20massive%20warehouse%20full%20of%20never-touched%2C%20vintage%20'80s%20sportswear%20from%20a%20family%20friend.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20had%2016%20days%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%20so%20they%20started%20selling%20it%20online.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Scottlynn%20Krause%2C%20the%20co-owner%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcs80vintage.squarespace.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECS80%20Vintage%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20best%20friend%20is%20Hannah%2C%20and%20her%20grandpa%2C%20Franz%2C%20owned%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fstay-warm-at-kids-sports-events%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esporting%20goods%20store%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20'60s%2C%20'70s%2C%20and%20'80s.%20When%20he%20went%20out%20of%20business%2C%20he%20boxed%20up%20his%20stock%2C%20and%20the%20unused%20items%20sat%20in%20a%20storage%20unit%20from%201990%20until%202021.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202021%2C%20Hannah's%20mom%20called%20my%20mom%2C%20who%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-swedish-death-cleaning-how-to-extreme-decluttering-method-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eorganizer%20for%20hoarders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20asking%20for%20help%20with%20the%20storage%20unit.%20She%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%20the%20stuff%2C%20and%20knew%20my%20mom%20had%20experience%20in%20that%20realm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2185353-4980-4754-8b78-c3330b9dfb71%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20did%20not%20expect%20to%20inherit%20his%20pristine%20'80s%20sportswear%20inventory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHannah%20and%20her%20family%20said%20to%20do%20what%20we%20needed%20to%20do%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20it%20and%20take%20it%20off%20the%20property.%20We%20had%2016%20days%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do%2C%20because%20they%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-ultra-wealthy-sell-mansions-whisper-listings-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elist%20the%20house%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20did%20not%20buy%20the%20inventory.%20It%20was%20a%20trade%20for%20removing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOriginally%2C%20my%20mom%20wanted%20to%20turn%20everything%20in%20three%20months%20and%20be%20done%20with%20it.%20We%20were%20not%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-sell-clothes-poshmark-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evintage-loving%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20then%2C%20but%20we%20decided%20to%20try%20to%20sell%20it%20online.%20At%20first%2C%20it%20was%20my%20mom%20doing%20it%20all%2C%20but%20it%20was%20overwhelming.%20So%20I%20jumped%20in.%20I%20had%20(and%20still%20have)%20a%20full-time%20job%20in%20retail%2C%20so%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20see%20what%20happens%20with%20trends.%20Vintage%20had%20picked%20up%2C%20so%20it%20felt%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f081fa62-cba4-46ff-9ace-474115fc067b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20storage%20unit%20had%20thousands%20of%20items%20from%20well-known%20brands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20really%20hard%20to%20put%20a%20number%20on%20how%20many%20items%20were%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboxes-storage-year-minimalism-move-interrupted-how-it-works-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estorage%20unit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%2010%2C000%20pairs%20of%20shoes%2C%2025%2C000%20hats%2C%202%2C500%20pairs%20of%20baseball%20pants%2C%20all%20in%201%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20all%20from%20a%20single%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brands%20Franz%20had%20were%20Nike%2C%20Adidas%2C%20Puma%2C%20Converse%2C%20Playboy%2C%20Pony%2C%20Champion%2C%20Wilson%2C%20and%20more.%20Teams%20were%20covered%20in%20the%20NFL%2C%20NBA%2C%20NHL%2C%20and%20collegiate%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20such%20a%20large%20inventory%3B%20we%20weren't%20sure%20how%20to%20tackle%20it.%20It's%20all%20been%20very%20word-of-mouth.%20We%20had%20our%20first%20sale%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclassic-thrift-stores-worse-secondhand-clothing-market-popular-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflea%20marke%3C%2Fa%3Et%20in%20early%202022.%20We%20currently%20sell%20privately%20on%20social%20media%20and%20on%20our%20website%2C%20which%20went%20live%20in%20December%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20website%2C%20we%20do%2025%20items%20per%20drop%2C%20and%20do%20two%20drops%20a%20week%2C%20on%20Wednesdays%20and%20Sundays.%20It's%20first-come%2C%20first-served.%20Not%20all%20merchandise%20is%20on%20the%20website%3B%20it's%20about%20a%20tenth%20of%20what%20we%20have.%20So%20we're%20really%20selective%20with%20the%20drops%20because%20everything%20is%20so%20rare%20and%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20store%20our%20inventory%20in%20an%20off-site%20warehouse.%20My%20mom%20and%20I%20go%20regularly%20to%20pull%20pieces%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20discovery%20every%20time.%20We%20never%20know%20what%20we%20are%20going%20to%20find.%20We%20then%20bring%20it%20to%20our%20studio%2C%20and%20I%20measure%2C%20photograph%2C%20and%20upload%20it%20to%20our%20website.%20My%20mom%20and%20I%20print%20the%20shipping%20labels%2C%20carefully%20pack%20each%20order%2C%20and%20ship%20everything%20ourselves%2C%20mostly%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20late%20at%20night%2C%20squeezed%20in%20around%20our%20day%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db2ea360-18a4-4988-9f8a-f1c1a6e7e1ab%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe've%20seen%20some%20really%20amazing%20items%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20our%20items%20are%20one-of-a-kind%2C%20making%20them%20special.%20We%20might%20have%20one%20item%20in%20multiple%20sizes%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20have%20four%20large%20sizes%20of%20that%20item%2C%20for%20example.%20Starter%20jackets%20are%20our%20most%20sought-after%20item.%20And%20our%20sports%20fans%20are%20die-hard%2C%20so%20people%20are%20freaking%20out%20about%20certain%20items.%20I%20didn't%20grow%20up%20during%20this%20time%20period.%20It's%20been%20so%20special%20to%20see%20the%20DMs%20we%20get%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20this%20shirt%20when%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20do%20you%20have%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20sold%20unique%20pieces%2C%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frun-dmc-member-says-sarah-mclachlan-saved-him-from-suicide-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERun-DMC%20collection%3C%2Fa%3E%20still%20in%20its%20original%20packaging%20and%20a%20rare%20pair%20of%201980s%20Adidas%20boxing%20shoes%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20Rocky%20Balboa%2FFreddie%20Mercury%20era.%20A%20van%20load%20of%20clothing%20from%20our%20collection%20was%20used%20on%20set%20for%20a%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ex%20Target%20commercial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22878d96c8-3372-4f8a-b002-405ec0b68778%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe've%20been%20having%20a%20blast%20doing%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20and%20dad%20met%20in%20a%20sporting%20goods%20store.%20He's%20a%20professional%20volleyball%20referee.%20My%20mom%20works%20as%20an%20organizer%20and%20is%20a%20photographer.%20I%20work%20in%20retail.%20All%20the%20pieces%20came%20together%20for%20us%2C%20giving%20us%20this%20gift.%20It%20was%20like%20winning%20the%20lotto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHannah's%20family%20loves%20watching%20it%20happen.%20I%20will%20send%20her%20pictures%20of%20stuff%20all%20the%20time.%20They%20are%20excited%20to%20see%20that%20his%20stuff%20is%20moving%2C%20going%20places%2C%20and%20getting%20a%20second%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20goal%20is%20to%20continue%20Franz's%20legacy%20by%20slowly%20placing%20these%20pieces%20with%20people%20who%20genuinely%20appreciate%20the%20memories%2C%20craftsmanship%2C%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%201980s.%20We're%20exploring%20ways%20to%20carry%20that%20energy%20forward%2C%20too.%20We%20eventually%20want%20to%20create%20our%20own%20products%20using%20our%20deadstock%20blanks%20to%20keep%20the%2080s%20aesthetic%20and%20story%20alive%20for%20the%20new%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finherited-1980s-vintage-sportswear-storage-unit-business-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772985721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a1cd921fb3fcb426489a83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finherited-1980s-vintage-sportswear-storage-unit-business-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20friend's%20grandfather%20boxed%20up%20his%20sporting%20goods%20store%20in%201990.%20Decades%20later%2C%20we%20found%20the%20untouched%20inventory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Finney%20Harden)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finherited-1980s-vintage-sportswear-storage-unit-business-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trisha%20Krishnan%20hits%20back%20on%20crude%20comments