2%3Esmaller%20European%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwo%20of%20my%20favorites%20are%20Cassis%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Tarragona%2C%20Spain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20my%20life%2C%20I've%20visited%20a%20total%20of%2018%20European%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20number%20climbed%20quickly%20when%20I%20moved%20from%20Chicago%20to%20London%20for%20college%20and%20spent%20four%20years%20living%20in%20my%20favorite%20city%2C%20thrilled%20by%20my%20newfound%20proximity%20to%20so%20many%20bucket-list%20destinations.%20Jumping%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrain-london-to-paris-first-class-eurostar-cabin-upgrade-review-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-and-a-half-hour%20train%20ride%20to%20Paris%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20a%2045-minute%20flight%20to%20Amsterdam%20never%20got%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I've%20explored%20big%20and%20small%20cities%2C%20I've%20been%20increasingly%20drawn%20to%20destinations%20beyond%20the%20major%20capitals%20that%20feel%20intimate%20and%20uncrowded.%20The%20more%20I've%20traveled%2C%20the%20more%20I've%20wanted%20to%20slow%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20underrated%20destinations%20in%20Europe%20I'd%20return%20to%20in%20a%20heartbeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECassis%2C%20France%2C%20is%20a%20postcard%20seaside%20town%20with%20access%20to%20a%20national%20park.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cassis%2C%20France%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a56bf31fb3fcb42648b595%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223167%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECassis%2C%20France.%3Cp%3Exbrchx%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20stopped%20in%20Cassis%20during%20a%20December%202025%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-winter-cruise-best-season-travel-to-mediterranean-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20cruise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%2