th%20of%20the%20Catalan%20capital%20along%20Spain's%20Golden%20Coast%2C%20Tarragona%20is%20a%20fascinating%20mix%20of%20historic%20Roman%20ruins%2C%20stunning%20beaches%2C%20and%20vibrant%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20one%20visit%2C%20a%20friend%20and%20I%20stopped%20in%20Tarragona%20for%20lunch%20at%20Osteria%20del%20Lab%2C%20where%20we%20indulged%20in%20the%20five-course%20tasting%20menu.%20Every%20dish%20was%20excellent%2C%20but%20the%20standout%20was%20a%20fresh%20shrimp-and-octopus%20salad%20drizzled%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-balsamic-vinegar-of-modena-is-made-in-italy-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebalsamic%20vinegar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20walked%20around%20and%20stopped%20at%20the%20Catedral%20de%20Tarragona%2C%20a%20Romanesque%20and%20Gothic%20church%20built%20between%20the%2012th%20and%2014th%20centuries%20located%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20historic%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20we%20couldn't%20skip%20the%20beach.%20I%20visited%20Playa%20el%20Miracle%2C%20which%20is%20within%20walking%20distance%20of%20the%20train%20station.%20Even%20when%20I%20was%20there%20in%20July%2C%20the%20middle%20of%20summer%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20many%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20search%20of%20a%20peaceful%20day%20by%20the%20water%2C%20Tarragona%20is%20worth%20a%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20skipped%20the%20summertime%20crowds%20in%20Skiathos%2C%20Greece.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226187%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Skiathos%2C%20Greece%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a56dddfd4fbd083f295057%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESkiathos%2C%20Greece%3Cp%3ESHansche%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20to%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fgreek-islands-to-visit-places-to-skip-from-frequent-traveler%23symi-is-the-perfe