oesn't%20love%20to%20complain%20about%20just%20about%20everything%3B%20he%20is%20an%20old%20man%20who%20spent%20decades%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moving-to-france-changed-lifestyle-eating-habits-grocery-shopping-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20France%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20all%2C%20but%20it's%20always%20with%20a%20cheeky%20tinge.%20The%20weather%20was%20particularly%20gruesome%20on%20his%20last%20visit.%20When%20in%20Rio%2C%20he%20complains%20because%20it's%20dangerous%2C%20loud%2C%20and%20unbearably%20hot.%20He%20jokes%20that%20he's%20going%20to%20move%20here%2C%20or%20we%20could%20swap%20houses%2C%20and%20honestly%2C%20I'm%20considering%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222fdf5fc5-457f-414d-8fd2-3b5f913bed45%5C%22%3EHe%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20early-stage%20Alzheimer's%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandfather%20was%2062%20when%20I%20was%20born%2C%20which%20means%20I%20got%20to%20know%20him%20as%20an%20adult.%20I%20get%20to%20take%20him%20to%20lunch%2C%20introduce%20him%20to%20my%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20they%20all%20love%20him%20%E2%80%94%20and%20hear%20his%20stories.%20I%20realize%20it%20isn't%20something%20everyone%20gets.%20For%20that%2C%20I%20am%20eternally%20grateful.%20It's%20easy%20to%20think%20that%20intergenerational%20relationships%20are%20most%20valuable%20in%20childhood%2C%20but%20they%20can%20flourish%20most%20in%20adulthood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20and%20grandfather%20at%20the%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a1c5091fb3fcb42648990b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20Portugal%2C%20my%20grandfather%20has%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20early-stage%20Alzheimer's.%20I%20witnessed%20him%20constantly%20searching%20for%20his%20wallet%20and%