%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Mexico%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20hearing%20great%20reviews%2C%20but%20I%20found%20the%20city%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20preferred%20visiting%20Santiago%20de%20Quer%C3%A9taro%20instead%2C%20a%20smaller%20city%20three%20hours%20away.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EQuer%C3%A9taro's%20historic%20center%20was%20charming%2C%20and%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20travel%20from%20there%20for%20day%20trips.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20planning%20my%20two-week%20trip%20to%20Mexico%2C%20I%20looked%20beyond%20destinations%20like%20Canc%C3%BAn%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-vallarta-cartel-american-retirement-paradise-nightmare-mexico-satellite-images-2026-02%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPuerto%20Vallarta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Cozumel.%20I%20wanted%20to%20visit%20central%20Mexico%20instead%2C%20which%20is%20further%20away%20from%20the%20busy%20cruise%20ports%20and%20all-inclusive%20resorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20I'd%20heard%20nothing%20but%20great%20things%20about%20Mexico%20City%2C%20so%20I%20put%20it%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20list.%20Travelers%20seem%20to%20always%20rave%20about%20the%20city's%20atmosphere%2C%20culinary%20scene%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-beautiful-museum-building-in-the-world-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworld-class%20museums%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20check%20it%20out%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20once%20I%20arrived%20in%20the%20city%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20about%2022%20million%20people%2C%20I%20was%20totally%20overwhelmed.%20The%20influx%20of%20tourists%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-dia-de-los-muertos-is-celebrated-around-the-world-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMexico's%20D%C3%ADa%20de%20Muertos%3C%2Fa%3E%20celebrations%20at%20the%20time%20probably%20didn't%20help%2C%20either.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20there%2C%20but%20I%20missed%20the%20quieter%20atmosphere%20of%20Santiago%20de%20Quer%C3%A9taro%2C%20where%20I'd%20been%20just%20a%20few%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Edays%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20smaller%20city%2C%20often%20shortened%20to%20just%20Quer%C3%A9taro%2C%20is%20home%20to%20around%201.5%20million%20people%20and%20is%20located%20just%20three%20hours%20by%20bus%20from%20Mexico%20City.%20I%20knew%20little%20about%20the%20area%20beforehand%2C%20but%20was%20soon%20blown%20away%20by%20its%20colorful%20historic%20center%20and%20nearby%20attractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMexico%20City%20gets%20a%20lot%20of%20hype%2C%20but%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%20was%20the%20city%20I'd%20previously%20barely%20heard%20of%20that%20exceeded%20my%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223961dbec-bbdb-48e0-ad60-42ebaf6e176a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuer%C3%A9taro's%20city%20center%20is%20exceptionally%20charming%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20people%20walking%20in%20Quere%CC%81taro%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a725b0d3e2f1aef369e71f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuere%CC%81taro%20is%20much%20smaller%20than%20Mexico%20City%2C%20but%20it%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20offer.%3Cp%3EJenna%20DeLaurentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20first%20morning%20in%20Quer%C3%A9taro%2C%20I%20was%20immediately%20struck%20by%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20the%20historic%20city%20center.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20designated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funesco-world-heritage-sites-us-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20Site%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it's%20full%20of%20tree-lined%20public%20squares.%20Each%20square%20acts%20as%20a%20meeting%20point%20for%20commerce%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20dining%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Figure%20with%20sugar%20skull%20head%20and%20colorful%20dress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a725b0d3e2f1aef369e71e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223808%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuere%CC%81taro's%20pedestrian-only%20streets%20are%20ideal%20for%20a%20relaxing%20walk.%3Cp%3EJenna%20DeLaurentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20dining%20outdoors%20in%20these%20public%20squares.%20Often%2C%20musicians%20played%20soft%20piano%20music%20during%20mealtimes%2C%20and%20the%20atmosphere%20was%20alluring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20squares%2C%20every%20street%20offered%20something%20new.%20On%20a%20visit%20to%20Quer%C3%A9taro's%20Museum%20of%20Arts%2C%20I%20was%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20building's%20Baroque-style%20architecture.%20The%20intricate%20design%20of%20the%20space%20was%20just%20as%20impressive%20as%20the%20artwork%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223935%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Quere%CC%81taro's%20Museum%20of%20Arts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a725b01fb3fcb42648d513%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222623%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuere%CC%81taro's%20Museum%20of%20Arts%20has%20stunning%20architecture.%3Cp%3EJenna%20DeLaurentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20a%20brief%20visit%20to%20the%20Calendar%20Museum%20left%20me%20impressed.%20The%20small%20museum%2C%20which%20houses%20exhibitions%20on%20time%20and%20space%2C%20contains%20intricately%20manicured%20gardens%20in%20a%20restored%20mansion.%20The%20space%20was%20serene%2C%20adding%20another%20special%20touch%20to%20Quer%C3%A9taro's%20endearing%20city%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20I%20found%20Mexico%20City%20to%20be%20more%20overwhelming%20than%20charming.%20With%20millions%20of%20people%2C%20cars%2C%20and%20buses%20zooming%20around%20every%20corner%2C%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20feel%20relaxed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20walking%20around%20Mexico%20City's%20maze%20of%20streets%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20missing%20the%20small-town%20feel%20of%20Quer%C3%A9taro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba41c074-6ba8-4938-8509-207dd242c39d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20city%20is%20a%20convenient%20home%20base%20for%20day%20trips%20to%20other%20destinations%2C%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22San%20Miguel%20de%20Allende%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a725b0d3e2f1aef369e71d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223808%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESan%20Miguel%20de%20Allende%20is%20a%20short%20drive%20from%20Quere%CC%81taro.%3Cp%3EJenna%20DeLaurentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESomething%20I%20loved%20during%20my%20time%20in%20Quer%C3%A9taro%20was%20the%20city's%20proximity%20to%20several%20exciting%20destinations.%20I%20found%20it%20easy%20to%20take%20a%20day%20(or%20overnight)%20trip%20from%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20visit%2C%20I%20took%20a%20one-night%20trip%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsan-miguel-de-allende-voted-best-city-in-the-world-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESan%20Miguel%20de%20Allende%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20small%20city%20with%20well-preserved%20colonial%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20perfect%20destination%20for%20a%20quick%20visit.%20I%20spent%20my%20time%20wandering%20around%20cobblestone%20streets%2C%20dining%20at%20rooftop%20cafes%2C%20and%20marveling%20at%20San%20Miguel%20de%20Allende's%20prominent%20pink%20cathedral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuer%C3%A9taro%20is%20also%20within%20an%20hour's%20drive%20to%20two%20of%20Mexico's%20Pueblo%20M%C3%A1gicos%2C%20or%20Magic%20Towns.%20There%20are%20177%20Pueblos%20M%C3%A1gicos%20within%20Mexico%2C%20and%20each%20town%20has%20been%20designated%20to%20have%20significant%20cultural%2C%20historical%2C%20or%20architectural%20significance%20within%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20these%20Pueblos%20M%C3%A1gicos%2C%20Bernal%2C%20is%20famous%20for%20its%20giant%20monolith%20that%20towers%20over%20the%20town.%20The%20other%2C%20Tequisquiapan%2C%20offers%20a%20peaceful%20getaway%20where%20visitors%20can%20explore%20traditional%20cheese%20markets%2C%20vineyards%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-most-beautiful-waters-in-the-world-to-visit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enatural%20hot%20springs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20day%20trips%20from%20Quer%C3%A9taro%20doesn't%20require%20a%20car%2C%20either.%20Uber%20is%20convenient%20throughout%20the%20area%2C%20and%20comfortable%20coach%20buses%20can%20take%20you%20from%20town%20to%20town%20at%20a%20low%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c51a9467-6970-4e33-a12c-b5d32e9749d8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMexico%20City%20has%20more%20to%20offer%20overall%2C%20but%20Quer%C3%A9taro%20is%20definitely%20worth%20a%20visit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Jenna%20DeLaurentis%20in%20Mexico%20City%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a725b0fd4fbd083f296ff5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223808%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20excited%20to%20check%20out%20Mexico%20City%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20my%20favorite%20place%20to%20visit%20in%20Mexico.%3Cp%3EJenna%20DeLaurentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20preferred%20Quer%C3%A9taro%20to%20Mexico%20City%2C%20there's%20no%20denying%20that%20there's%20far%20more%20to%20see%20and%20do%20in%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20spend%20months%20in%20Mexico%20City%20and%20barely%20scratch%20the%20surface.%20The%20city%20has%20over%20150%20museums%20and%20galleries%20along%20with%20the%20palatial%20Chapultepec%20Castle%2C%20massive%20Z%C3%B3calo%20Square%2C%20vast%20green%20parks%2C%20and%20more%20restaurants%20than%20you%20could%20try%20in%20a%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20National%20Museum%20of%20Anthropology%20could%20take%20an%20entire%20day%20to%20see%20in%20and%20of%20itself!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expected%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20Mexico%20City%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20jive%20with%20the%20city%20as%20much%20as%20I%20thought%20I%20would.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20though%2C%20I'd%20still%20agree%20that%20Mexico%20City%20is%20worth%20the%20hype%20it%20receives.%20The%20metropolis%20has%20an%20addictive%2C%20bustling%20atmosphere%2C%20and%20the%20street-food%20scene%20is%20definitely%20out%20of%20this%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20my%20trip%20was%20a%20good%20reminder%20to%20look%20beyond%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-50-countries-tourism-ranked-worst-to-best-frequent-traveler-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20popular%20destinations%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20particular%20place.%20I%20had%20never%20even%20heard%20of%20Quer%C3%A9taro%20before%20I%20planned%20my%20trip%2C%20but%20I'm%20so%20glad%20I%20took%20the%20chance%20to%20discover%20somewhere%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskip-mexico-city-where-to-go-instead-nearby-queretaro-tips-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772975641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a726161fb3fcb42648d52d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskip-mexico-city-where-to-go-instead-nearby-queretaro-tips-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mexico%20City%20was%20too%20crowded%20for%20me.%20So%2C%20I'm%20glad%20I%20had%20Santiago%20de%20Quer%C3%A9taro%2C%20a%20smaller%20city%20just%20a%20short%20bus%20ride%20away%2C%20on%20my%20travel%20itinerary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jenna%20DeLaurentis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskip