EMelina%20Mara%20-%20Pool%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBecoming%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20justice%20is%20the%20culmination%20of%20decades%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20legal%20expertise.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20it%20comes%20with%20notable%20perks%2C%20including%20a%20high%20salary%2C%20prestige%2C%20and%20lifetime%20security.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20also%20the%20private%20basketball%20court.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20great%20time%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmajority-dont-trust-the-supreme-court-and-want-term-limits-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Supreme%20Court%20justice%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2025%2F09%2F03%2Ffavorable-views-of-supreme-court-remain-near-historic-low%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20in%20August%202025%20found%20that%20half%20of%20Americans%20surveyed%20held%20%26quot%3Ban%20unfavorable%20opinion%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20with%20favorable%20opinions%20%26quot%3Bclose%20to%20a%20three-decade%20low.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20current%20president%20isn't%20happy%20with%20the%20court%20either.%20After%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-reaction-supreme-court-scotus-tariff-ruling-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESCOTUS%20ruled%20against%20his%20emergency%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20the%20justices%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20ashamed%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20he%20later%20exchanged%20cordial%20handshakes%20with%20them%20at%20the%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20all%20bad.%20Supreme%20Court%20historian%20and%20University%20of%20Texas%20law%20professor%20Lucas%20%26quot%3BScot%26quot%3B%20Powe%20told%20%3Ca%20