0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-open-concept-home-interior-designers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eopen-concept%20layout%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20which%20combined%20the%20kitchen%2C%20dining%20area%2C%20and%20living%20area%20into%20a%20single%20rectangular%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInitially%2C%20I%20loved%20the%20open%20concept%20because%20I%20was%20just%20young%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20it%20looks%20so%20big%20and%20open%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%20that%20kind%20of%20changed%20over%20time%2C%20especially%20with%20two%20toddlers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOcchipinti%20said%20that%20as%20her%20living%20room%20started%20to%20double%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-has-designed-over-1000-playrooms-shares-her-tips-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplay%20space%20for%20her%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20whole%20main%20floor%20felt%20less%20inviting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20concept%20dining%20and%20living%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9eeee1fb3fcb426490255%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20main%20floor%20was%20open%20concept.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Occhipinti%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20see%20toys%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Occhipinti%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20overstimulating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20since%20the%20TV%20was%20visible%20from%20the%20table%2C%20she%20said%20her%20children%20would%20try%20to%20watch%20it%20while%20they%20ate%20meals%2C%20which%20she%20didn't%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20time%20for%20a%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b62b39e-5e3a-42aa-95c9-b0a122563f76%5C%22%3EA%20new%20layout%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOcchipinti%20wasn't%20a%20stranger%20to%20enclosing%20spaces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22