anted%20it%20to%20be%20open%20and%20airy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9687437-f35d-43eb-ae3e-e9f1572f4c17%5C%22%3EA%20partial%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOcchipinti%20wasn't%20sure%20how%20to%20break%20up%20her%20space%20until%20she%20stumbled%20upon%20some%20Pinterest%20images%20of%20pony%20walls%2C%20a%20half%20wall%20that%20can%20divide%20a%20space%20while%20keeping%20it%20partially%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20thought%20it%20could%20be%20a%20perfect%20fit%20for%20her%20home%2C%20as%20it%20could%20make%20the%20living%20area%20feel%20separate%20while%20still%20maintaining%20an%20open%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOcchipinti%20tapped%20Primespec%20Construction%20again%20to%20handle%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-transformed-open-concept-living-room-kitchen-glass-wall-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erenovation%20of%20her%20living%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sending%20them%20her%20inspiration%20images.%20It%20took%20just%20one%20day%20and%20%242%2C500%20to%20put%20up%20the%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20got%20there%20at%20like%209%3A30%20and%20the%20wall%20was%20built%20and%20done%20by%20like%204%3A30%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dining%20room%20with%20a%20pony%20wall%20separating%20it%20from%20the%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9ef15fd4fbd083f299d0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20wall%20sits%20between%20the%20dining%20and%20living%20room.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Occhipinti%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20white%20pony%20wall%20dividing%20the%20living%20room%20from%20the%20kitchen%20and%20dining%20area%20has%20a%20column%20on%20one%20side%20and%20molding%20for%20a%20design%20pop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOcchipinti%20has%20the%20couch%20leaning%20against%20one%20wall%2C%20and%20the%20dining%20table%20on%2