o%20in%20Milan.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cindy%20Sheahan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20Census%20data%20shows%20that%20net%20immigration%20to%20the%20US%20has%20tumbled.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20spoken%20with%20dozens%20of%20Americans%20who%20have%20moved%20abroad.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFour%20women%20over%2050%20who%20moved%20to%20Europe%20share%20why%20living%20abroad%20is%20better%20for%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECindy%20Sheahan%20was%20at%20a%20crossroads.%20Friends%20and%20loved%20ones%20were%20passing%20away%2C%20and%20her%20marriage%20was%20starting%20to%20unravel.%20She%20could%20feel%20life%20passing%20her%20by%20%E2%80%94%20and%20after%20years%20spent%20raising%20her%20kids%2C%20she%20decided%20it%20was%20finally%20time%20to%20put%20herself%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20figured%20I'd%20start%20traveling%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheahan%2C%2064%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BMy%20company%20was%20kind%20enough%20to%20let%20me%20take%20a%20sabbatical%20while%20I%20sorted%20out%20my%20world.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20mistake%20for%20them%2C%20because%20I%20decided%20I%20wasn't%20coming%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20several%20years%2C%20Sheahan%2C%20now%20divorced%2C%20has%20traveled%20to%20nearly%2050%20countries%2C%20including%20Laos%2C%20Portugal%2C%20Madagascar%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20Vietnam.%20In%202025%2C%20she%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaving-us-for-italy-retire-in-sicily-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPalermo%2C%20Sicily%2C%20her%20home%20base%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20while%20she%20plans%20to%20visit%20the%20US%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20she%20says%20she%20won't%20be%20moving%20back%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I%20outgrew%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20and%20places%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheahan%20said.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20get%20me%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20I%20desperately%20miss%20my%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20especially%20my%20kids.%20But%20they're%20all%20able%20to%20travel%2C%20and%20they'd%20much%20rather%20visit%20me%20somewhere%20fun%20than%20grab%20a%20drink%20at%20a%20bar%20in%20Denver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Italy%2C%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20eat%20better%2C%20I've%20made%20new%20friends%2C%20I've%20cut%20down%20on%20expenses%20%E2%80%94%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20I'm%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22caa07f94-5519-497c-a60f-6a80d31dd2b1%5C%22%3EMore%20people%20are%20moving%20out%20of%20the%20US%2C%20and%20fewer%20are%20moving%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECensus%20Bureau%20data%20shows%20that%20net%20international%20migration%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%2C%20arrivals%20minus%20departures%20%E2%80%94%20hit%20a%20high%20of%202.7%20million%20in%202024.%20By%20July%202025%2C%20that%20number%20had%20dropped%20to%201.3%20million%2C%20and%20if%20the%20current%20trajectory%20holds%2C%20the%20Bureau%20forecasts%20it%20could%20fall%20again%20to%20about%20321%2C000%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20those%20trends%20continue%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20the%20United%20States%20has%20seen%20net%20negative%20migration%20in%20more%20than%2050%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Bureau%20said%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bureau%20attributes%20the%20change%20to%20two%20trends%20moving%20in%20opposite%20directions%3A%20fewer%20people%20immigrating%20to%20the%20US%2C%20and%20more%20people%20leaving%20the%20country%20to%20live%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F9eEgS%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Net%20international%20migration%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22329%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20I've%20spoken%20with%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20Americans%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20them%20women%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-moved-to-spain-business-helping-black-women-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhy%20they%20moved%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20mention%20the%20same%20mix%20of%20reasons%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivorced-retired-in-europe-paris-italy-pros-cons-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20has%20become%20too%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20want%20to%20step%20away%20from%20work%20and%20build%20lives%20that%20feel%20more%20meaningful.%20It%20led%20them%20to%20places%20like%20Panama%2C%20Spain%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftirana-albania-underrated-tourist-expat-destination-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlbania%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECepee%20Tabibian%2C%20a%20Spain-based%20relocation%20coach%20who%20has%20helped%20many%20Americans%20move%20overseas%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20her%20female%20clients%20are%20also%20worried%20about%20the%20political%20climate%20in%20the%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%2C%20I%20think%20people%20just%20wanted%20to%20move%20for%20a%20better%20quality%20of%20life%3B%20to%20fulfill%20a%20dream%2C%20to%20have%20a%20softer%20life.%20But%20now%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20are%20coming%20up%20for%20people%20are%20related%20to%20the%20political%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20stories%20of%20four%20women%20I%20spoke%20with%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaving-usa-live-abroad-reverse-culture-shock-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhy%20they%20left%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20their%20lives%20have%20changed%20since%2C%20for%20better%20and%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262d77c34-c6d2-4e5f-9497-e94a97b95227%5C%22%3EHigh%20living%20costs%20have%20pushed%20some%20women%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou've%20probably%20noticed%20how%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprices-food-coffee-gas-clothes-pets-rent-survey-inflation-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20expensive%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20has%20gotten.%20Data%20show%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-biggest-economic-mistake-prices-affordability-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20prices%20are%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%2025%25%20since%202020.%20For%20older%20single%20women%2C%20that%20can%20make%20it%20especially%20hard%20to%20get%20by%2C%20particularly%20when%20Social%20Security%20is%20their%20main%20source%20of%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Sheahan%2C%20moving%20abroad%20was%20partially%20a%20financial%20decision.%20She%20has%20savings%20and%20investments%2C%20but%20in%20retirement%2C%20her%20most%20dependable%20income%20is%20the%20%241%2C500%20she%20receives%20each%20month%20in%20Social%20Security.%20In%20Denver%2C%20that%20wouldn't%20have%20covered%20rent.%20In%20Palermo%2C%20it%20pays%20for%20her%20%24800-a-month%20apartment%20and%20still%20leaves%20room%20for%20groceries%20and%20nights%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20that%20I%20can%20go%20to%20the%20grocery%20store%20and%20not%20break%20the%20bank.%20You%20can%20buy%20tomatoes%2C%20eggplants%2C%20zucchini%2C%20sundried%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20everything%20else%20for%20a%20song%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Healthcare%20has%20been%20cheaper%20for%20her%2C%20too%3B%20seeing%20a%20specialist%20costs%20her%20about%20%2440.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20woman%2C%20side%20by%20side%20with%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9d388fd4fbd083f29997a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESandy%20Adam%20and%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower.%3Cp%3ESandy%20Adam%2F%20Getty%20Images%2F%20Elena%20Zolotova%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESandy%20Adam%20can%20relate.%20After%20she%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-from-tech-job-retired-france-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%20from%20her%20tech%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202025%2C%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20find%20another%20role%20and%20retired.%20But%20the%20idea%20of%20living%20on%20just%20her%20%243%2C608-a-month%20Social%20Security%20benefit%20back%20in%20Pittsburgh%20made%20her%20nervous%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20annual%20property%20taxes%20of%20about%20%246%2C900%20on%20her%201%2C700-square-foot%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20myself%3A%20If%20I%20tried%20to%20live%20off%20Social%20Security%2C%20could%20I%20afford%20to%20stay%20in%20that%20house%3F%20I%20probably%20could%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20really%20tight%2C%26quot%3B%20Adam%2C%2069%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BLong-term%2C%20though%2C%20the%20financial%20predictability%20felt%20increasingly%20uncertain%20%E2%80%94%20my%20everyday%20living%20expenses%20like%20groceries%20were%20going%20up%20too.%20I%20wanted%20to%20simplify%20my%20life%2C%20with%20fewer%20fixed%20costs%20and%20fewer%20surprises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20moving%20to%20Europe%20was%20%26quot%3Bmore%20practical%26quot%3B%20than%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20work%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20now%20lives%20in%20Chatou%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20Paris%2C%20renting%20a%20548-square-foot%2C%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20with%20her%20dog.%20She%20pays%20%241%2C679%20a%20month%2C%20and%20while%20she%20says%20it%20still%20feels%20a%20little%20expensive%2C%20it's%20given%20her%20%26quot%3Ba%20soft%20landing%26quot%3B%20while%20she%20figures%20out%20where%20she%20ultimately%20wants%20to%20settle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d445e9cd-4961-42f7-bef7-5b7faabae657%5C%22%3ESome%20women%20want%20to%20reinvent%20themselves%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20women%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20retirement%2C%20moving%20overseas%20also%20gives%20them%20a%20chance%20to%20reinvent%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20living%20your%20same%20exact%20life%20in%20a%20different%20destination%2C%26quot%3B%20Tabibian%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20women%20who%20come%20to%20me%20want%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20maybe%20spend%20some%20time%20re-getting%20to%20know%20themselves%2C%20or%20take%20the%20time%20to%20try%20something%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20poses%20with%20her%20dog.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9d447fd4fbd083f29999a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENatalie%20Lynch%20and%20her%20dog%20Enzo.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Natalie%20Lynch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENatalie%20Lynch%20had%20been%20working%20since%20she%20was%2015.%20Burned%20out%20and%20priced%20out%20of%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20wind%20down%20her%20home-staging%20business%20of%2024%20years%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-who-moved-to-europe-shares-the-pros-and-cons-of-her-new-life-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%2C%20hoping%20for%20a%20more%20relaxed%20and%20purposeful%20life%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20a%20lower%20cost%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pandemic%2C%20with%20its%20loss%20of%20freedom%2C%20loss%20of%20connectivity%2C%20and%20the%20very%20clear%20message%20that%20life%20can%20be%20short%2C%20was%20a%20real%20wake-up%20call%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Lynch%2C%2056%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20decided%20I%20needed%20to%20make%20some%20big%20changes%2C%20even%20if%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20clear%20idea%20of%20what%20the%20endgame%20would%20look%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20time%20in%20Europe%20hasn't%20been%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20bounced%20between%20Italy%2C%20Spain%2C%20and%2C%20most%20recently%2C%20France.%20With%20only%20her%20dog%2C%20Enzo%2C%20as%20her%20travel%20companion%2C%20she's%20felt%20lonely%20at%20times%2C%20and%20navigating%20European%20bureaucracy%20has%20been%20challenging%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20since%20she%20isn't%20fluent%20in%20Spanish%20or%20French.%20Still%2C%20she%20said%2C%20escaping%20her%20hectic%20life%20and%20the%20rising%20costs%20back%20home%20has%20been%20life-changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20don't%20think%20I'm%20living%20my%20best%20life%20here%2C%20it's%20a%20better%20life%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-california-better-healthcare-portugal-cheaper-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20had%20in%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I'm%20headed%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20figured%20it%20all%20out%20yet%2C%20but%20the%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%2C%20not%20having%20to%20grind%20every%20day%20running%20a%20business%2C%20and%20being%20out%20of%20the%20rat%20race%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20gift.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20with%20glasses%20has%20a%20big%20grin%20on%20her%20face%20as%20she%20walks%20down%20a%20street.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9d4e51fb3fcb42648fee8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDawn%20Belisle.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dawn%20Belisle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20gifting%20herself%20a%20birthday%20trip%20to%20Paris%20in%202019%20%E2%80%94%20complete%20with%20a%20French%20baking%20workshop%20%E2%80%94%20Dawn%20Belisle%2C%20an%20attorney%20and%20part-time%20pastry%20chef%20from%20Atlanta%2C%20fell%20so%20in%20love%20with%20France%20that%20she%20moved%20there%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20spirit%20felt%20at%20peace%20there%20in%20a%20way%20that's%20hard%20to%20describe%2C%26quot%3B%20Belisle%2C%2056%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20was%20just%20living.%20They're%20out%20and%20about%2C%20enjoying%20each%20other's%20company.%20They%20sit%20at%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20eating%20and%20drinking%20together.%20They%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20hustle-and-bustle%20culture%20we%20have%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelisle%20now%20lives%20in%20the%20Carr%C3%A9%20d'Or%2C%20one%20of%20Nice's%20pricier%2C%20livelier%20neighborhoods.%20She%20spends%20her%20days%20walking%20the%20beach%2C%20shopping%20local%20markets%20for%20fresh%20produce%2C%20and%20lingering%20at%20caf%C3%A9s%20with%20her%20French%20and%20Italian%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%20to%20work%20as%20an%20attorney%2C%20consulting%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20offices%2C%20but%20France%20has%20also%20opened%20the%20door%20to%20her%20second%20act%3A%20creating%20a%20lifestyle%20brand%20where%20she%20posts%20style%20and%20travel%20content%20and%20mentors%20people%20considering%20a%20move%20abroad.%20It's%20given%20her%20a%20new%20sense%20of%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20peace%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-french-coast-from-london-benefits-downsides-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20have%20in%20France%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20unbeatable%2C%26quot%3B%20Belisle%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20do%20a%20lot%20and%20keep%20a%20schedule%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20more%20in%20control%20of%20my%20life%20here.%20I'm%20living%20to%20live%20instead%20of%20work%2C%20and%20I'm%20exploring%20more.%20To%20me%2C%20that's%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMadison%20Hoff%2C%20a%20reporter%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20economy%20team%2C%20contributed%20to%20this%20article.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20hre