%26quot%3B%20as%20they%20pour%20huge%20sums%20into%20building%20out%20AI%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20bull%26quot%3B%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthomas-kaplan-gold-silver-price-outlook-paulson-novagold-buffett-investing-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egold%20and%20silver%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20he%20said%2C%20as%20government%20policies%20around%20the%20world%20have%20eroded%20the%20value%20of%20national%20currencies%2C%20and%20he's%20reluctant%20to%20%26quot%3Bjump%20on%20the%20crypto%20bandwagon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMellon%20said%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-stock-picks-energy-market-oil-utilities-sector-outperforms-buy-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenergy%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20probably%20the%20best%20place%20to%20invest%26quot%3B%20right%20now%2C%20partly%20because%20the%20AI%20boom%20is%20fueling%20demand%20for%20power-hungry%20data%20centers%20and%20straining%20electric%20grids%2C%20and%20partly%20because%20he%20sees%20energy%20as%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20underpriced%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20world%20stock%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20bargains%20to%20be%20had%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20in%20emerging%20markets%2C%20he%20said.%20But%20he%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bvery%2C%20very%20careful%20in%20China%26quot%3B%20given%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-economy-chinese-stock-market-foreign-investor-cash-flow-money-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehazards%20of%20foreign%20ownership%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20state%20control%2C%20and%20would%20%26quot%3Btotally%20avoid%20the%20US%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recommended%20people%20hold%20Japanese%20yen%20as%20it's%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20cheap%26quot%3B%20versus%20the%20dollar%2C%20and%20yielding%20more%20than%20in%20the%20past%20thanks%20to%20rising%20inter