ong-form%20articles%20with%20friends%20or%20followers%20might%20increase%20commitment%20to%20the%20goal%20of%20reading%20or%20watching%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de31afc5-c6aa-452d-8fca-ed13bf203ca9%5C%22%3ESocial%20cataloging%20apps%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bmedia%20I've%20consumed%20this%20week%20instead%20of%20doomscrolling%26quot%3B%20trend%20coincides%20with%20the%20growing%20popularity%20of%20social%20cataloging%20apps%20among%20Gen%20Z.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20February%2C%20the%20film%20cataloging%20platform%20Letterboxd%20has%20over%2027%20million%20members%2C%20up%20from%2017%20million%20this%20time%20last%20year%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20its%20fans%20skew%20young.%20Data%20from%20its%20recent%20surveys%20and%20Google%20Analytics%20showed%20that%20its%20core%20members%20are%20aged%20between%2018%20and%2035%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202007%20and%20acquired%20by%20Amazon%20in%202013%2C%20Goodreads%20has%20more%20than%20150%20million%20members%2C%20according%20to%20an%20estimate%20in%202023.%20Goodreads%20did%20not%20provide%20more%20recent%20data%20in%20response%20to%20a%20request%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fwhat-is-goodreads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emonopoly%20over%20the%20book-tracking%20world%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20prompted%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20host%20of%20other%20book%20logging%20apps%2C%20such%20as%20The%20StoryGraph%20and%20Fable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENadia%20Odunayo%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20The%20StoryGraph%2C%20which%20hit%205%20million%20user%20signups%20at%20the%20end%20of%20January%20after%20launching%20in%202019%2C%20said%20the%20platform%20has%20helped%20people%20read%20more%20%E2%80%94%20including%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20StoryGraph%20has%20functions%20such%20as%20book%20discovery%20based%20on%20mood%20and%20options%20for%20rating%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20lots%20of%20people%20finding%2C%20rediscovering%2C%20the%20love%20of%20reading%20that%20they%20used%20to%20have%20as%20a%20kid.%20That's%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20Odunayo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20saying%2C%20'I%20used%20to%20read%20as%20a%20kid%2C%20and%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20I%20hardly%20read.%20I%20would%20manage%20one%20book%20a%20year%2C%20and%20now%20I've%20read%2060%2C%2070%2C%2080%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Books%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0b3a31fb3fcb426488918%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224128%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EColmenares%20recommends%20books%20she%20has%20enjoyed%20on%20her%20page%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20Doomscrolling.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENathalia%20Angarita%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%2C%20the%20appeal%20of%20logging%20and%20sharing%20the%20media%20they%20consume%20is%20about%20understanding%20what%20their%20tastes%20say%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20less%20about%20finding%20new%20content%20to%20get%20into%20and%20recommendations%20%E2%80%94%20more%20so%20a%20focus%20on%20understanding%20yourself%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20your%20consumption%2C%20in%20your%20case%2C%20and%20understanding%20others%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20their%20consumption%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jad%20Esber%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20social%20cataloging%20app%20Shelf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20critics%20see%20an%20element%20of%20performativity%20in%20the%20trend%20%E2%80%94%20turning%20media%20consumption%20into%20another%20metric%20to%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20carefully%20curated%20nature%20of%20the%20posts%20and%20their%20public%20visibility%20raises%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20logging%20what%20you%20read%20is%20meaningfully%20different%20from%20other%20forms%20of%20personal%20branding%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Colmenares%2C%20writing%20about%20her%20online%20media%20consumption%20has%20had%20a%20tangible%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanalog-bags-tiktok-trend-replacing-screen-time-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoffline%20effect%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20allowed%20me%20to%20read%20a%20lot%20more%2C%20write%20more%20in%20my%20journal%2C%20and%20do%20more%20offline%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20drawing%20again.%20I'm%20doing%20all%20of%20these%20things%20that%20I%20used%20to%20do%20but%20couldn't%2C%20because%20I%20was%20so%20addicted%20to%20my%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-doomscrolling-tracking-film-podcasts-books-analog-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772966341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0b433d3e2f1aef3699bc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-doomscrolling-tracking-film-podcasts-books-analog-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fed%20up%20with%20endless%20scrolling%2C%20some%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20tracking%20their%20media%20consumption%20to%20be%20more%20intentional%20about%20their%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rshahidi%40insider.com%20(Roya%20Shahidi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-doomscrolling-tracking-film-podcasts-books-analog-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20brains%20behind%20BI's%20new%20must-read%20newsletter%20explains%20why%20every%20marketer%20needs%20it%20in%20their%20inbox%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20what%20OpenAI%20said%20is%20a%20fake%20ad%5C%22%20char