.com%2Fmrbeast-former-manager-says-age-of-social-giants-is-fading-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20age%20of%20social-media%20superstars%20is%20fading%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20There%20might%20not%20be%20another%20MrBeast%20as%20we%20know%20it.%20What's%20the%20next%20evolution%20in%20the%20creator%20economy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20high-profile%20individual%20creators%20%E2%80%94%20or%20troupes%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdude-perfect-hired-first-content-chief-build-next-disney-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDude%20Perfect%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20morphing%20to%20become%20media%20and%20entertainment%20businesses%2C%20with%20professionalized%20corporate%20structures.%20At%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20scale%2C%20we're%20seeing%20the%20rise%20of%20niche%20creators%20with%20more%20people%20making%20money%20from%20posting%20content%20online%20than%20ever.%20Big%20brands%20are%20responding%20by%20taking%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funilever-20x-influencer-mandate-sparks-creator-marketing-gold-rush-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnilever's%20book%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20dramatically%20upping%20their%20influencer%20marketing%20budgets.%20It%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20all%20creators%20are%20getting%20big%20paydays%2C%20however%2C%20because%20the%20marketplace%20has%20become%20so%20saturated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20your%20first%20edition%2C%20you%20highlighted%20an%20absolutely%20wild%20story%20of%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-hoax-ad-mystery-takes-a-new-twist-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20mystery%20surrounding%20an%20OpenAI%20device%20ad%20hoax%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20and%20a%20recent%20new%20twist.%20What's%20your%20theory%20on%20what's%20going%20on%20here%20and%20how%20this%20all%20plays%20out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's