mtrak%20bedroom%20with%20a%20bunk%20bed%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69987b14156648bc16a89564%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOvernight%20Amtrak%20trains%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoach-amtrak-ride-vancouver-to-seattle-surprising-things-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoach%20seating%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sleeper%20cabins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20going%20to%20sincerely%20enjoy%20two%20nights%20on%20a%20train%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20comfortable.%20So%20I%20didn't%20regret%20splurging%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-private-bedroom-roomettes-family-review-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprivate%20bedroom%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20my%2053-hour%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20%242%2C200%2C%20the%20roughly%2050-square-foot%20space%20packed%20in%20a%20foldout%20sofa%2C%20an%20upper%20bunk%2C%20a%20seat%2C%20a%20pullout%20table%2C%20a%20full%20bathroom%2C%20and%20a%20closet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20space%20that%20was%20my%20own%20made%20this%20trip%20so%20much%20more%20relaxing%20than%20it%20would%20have%20been%20in%20coach.%20I%20especially%20appreciated%20having%20a%20full%20private%20bathroom%2C%20an%20amenity%20available%20only%20in%20bedrooms%20on%20Amtrak%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20bedroom%20is%20out%20of%20your%20budget%2C%20consider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-superliner-train-roomette-tour-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebooking%20a%20roomette%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20overnight%20ride.%20It's%20a%20smaller%20private%20cabin%20without%20a%20bathroom%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20woke%20up%20with%20the%20sun%20on%20departure%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sun%20rises%20over%20the%20lake%20in%20Chicago%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8adb5d3e2f1aef36a0264%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20thing%20I've%20learned%20about%20myself%20through%20overnight%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisappointing-photos-show-what-train-travel-is-like-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrain%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20nothing%20spoils%20my%20mindset%20like%20a%20restless%20night.%20I%20wanted%20to%20set%20myself%20up%20for%20sleep%20success%20on%20the%20California%20Zephyr.%20So%20even%20though%20my%20train%20didn't%20leave%20Chicago%20until%202%20p.m.%2C%20I%20set%20my%20alarm%20for%206%20a.m.%20on%20the%20day%20of%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20tired%20I%20am%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurns%20out%2C%20my%20plan%20worked.%20I%20dozed%20off%20easily%20on%20the%20train%20and%20got%20seven%20to%20eight%20hours%20of%20sleep%20each%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20spent%20the%20morning%20on%20my%20feet.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cross%20walk%20with%20construction%20on%20the%20left%20beneath%20a%20bridge%20in%20Chicago%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8adeed3e2f1aef36a0269%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20several%20hours%20to%20kill%20before%20my%20afternoon%20train.%20I%20spent%20them%20walking%20around%20Chicago%20and%20the%20surrounding%20areas.%20I%20wanted%20to%20wear%20out%20my%20legs%20and%20soak%20in%20as%20much%20fresh%20air%20as%20possible%20before%20spending%20the%20better%20part%20of%2053%20hours%20in%20a%2050-square-foot%20enclosed%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20boarded%20the%20train%2C%20I%20was%20grateful%20for%20the%20chance%20to%20sit%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAmtrak%20provided%20my%20meals%2C%20but%20I%20packed%20my%20own%20snacks.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20packaged%20snacks%20on%20a%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8b0befd4fbd083f298b87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fovernight-amtrak-viewliner-roomette-vs-bedroom-comparison%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmtrak%20sleeper%20accommodations%3C%2Fa%3E%20come%20with%20complimentary%20meals%20served%20in%20the%20dining%20car%2C%20and%20passengers%20can%20purchase%20snacks%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-food-review-cafe-car-menu-prices-photos-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecaf%C3%A9%20car%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20glad%20I%20packed%20my%20own%20snacks%20for%20in%20between%20meals%20because%20I%20saved%20some%20money%20I%20would%20have%20spent%20at%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20car.%20I%20also%20brought%20a%20variety%20of%20options%20to%20satisfy%20every%20craving.%20Chips%2C%20granola%20bars%2C%20trail%20mix%2C%20stroopwafels%2C%20chocolate%2C%20and%20gummies%20were%20nearly%20devoured%20by%20the%20end%20of%20my%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20brought%20multiple%20activities%20to%20pass%20the%20time.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20a%20notebook%2C%20phone%2C%20and%20Nintendo%20on%20a%20table%20and%20the%20author%20reading%20a%20book%20on%20the%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a98065fd4fbd083f298fa4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20being%20stuck%20on%20the%20rails%20feels%20like%20reliving%20the%20same%20hour%20over%20and%20over%20again.%20Avoiding%20boredom%20was%20important%20to%20me%20for%20the%20longest%20train%20ride%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20settled%20into%20my%20room%2C%20I%20made%20a%20list%20of%20all%20the%20ways%20I%20could%20spend%20my%20time%20and%20planned%20to%20swap%20activities%20every%20hour%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPacking%20a%20variety%20of%20things%20to%20do%20and%20being%20intentional%20about%20blocking%20out%20time%20for%20each%20made%20my%20days%20feel%20more%20structured%20and%20fulfilling.%20I%20brought%20a%20book%2C%20a%20journal%2C%20my%20Nintendo%20Switch%2C%20two%20cameras%2C%20and%20my%20work%20laptop.%20(I%20also%20packed%20a%20musical%20instrument%20to%20pass%20the%20time%2C%20but%20that%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-california-zephyr-mistakes-to-avoid-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emistake%20I'd%20avoid%20next%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESlippers%20and%20Crocs%20were%20worth%20packing%2C%20too.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20author's%20feet%20in%20slippers%20next%20to%20a%20pair%20of%20Crocs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a981a11fb3fcb42648f4ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20travel%2C%20I%20usually%20find%20it's%20worth%20it%20to%20pack%20comforts%20of%20home.%20I%20wear%20my%20slippers%20all%20day%20around%20my%20apartment%2C%20so%20wearing%20them%20in%20my%20train%20bedroom%20calmed%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Crocs%20served%20two%20purposes%20on%20this%20trip.%20I%20wore%20them%20in%20the%20shower%20to%20protect%20my%20feet%20from%20germs%2C%20and%20I%20wore%20them%20to%20walk%20around%20the%20train.%20It%20was%20much%20easier%20to%20slide%20them%20on%20than%20to%20lace%20up%20my%20chunky%20boots%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20other%20pair%20of%20shoes%20I%20had%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20had%20the%20Crocs%2C%20I%20tucked%20my%20boots%20away%20into%20the%20closet%20until%20the%20end%20of%20my%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUtilizing%20the%20top%20bunk%20made%20the%20space%20feel%20bigger.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223556%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20lies%20smiling%20in%20the%20top%20bunk%20in%20the%20Amtrak%20bedroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69977f2fa645d1188189a21f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20so%20fond%20of%20the%20top%20bunk%20after%20night%20one%20that%20I%20kept%20it%20down%20throughout%20the%20next%20day.%20In%20such%20a%20small%20room%2C%20having%20one%20more%20space%20to%20hang%20out%20meant%20a%20lot%20to%20me.%20I%20had%20the%20couch%2C%20the%20chair%2C%20and%20now%20the%20top%20bunk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20day%2C%20I%20sat%20on%20the%20couch%20or%20the%20seat%20to%20write%20and%20work%20on%20my%20computer.%20When%20I%20wanted%20to%20play%20video%20games%20or%20read%2C%20I%20climbed%20the%20ladder%20to%20use%20the%20top%20bunk%20as%20a%20cozy%20loft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20a%20train%20without%20WiFi%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20I'd%20still%20be%20able%20to%20watch%20TV%20before%20bed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holds%20a%20phone%20playing%20anime%20in%20a%20dark%20room%20with%20a%20dim%2C%20blue%20light%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a981dad3e2f1aef36a06dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20Amtrak%20trains%20I've%20been%20on%2C%20the%20California%20Zephyr%20doesn't%20have%20WiFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20TV-before-bed%20person%2C%20I%20downloaded%20sitcoms%20and%20anime%20episodes%20from%20Netflix%20before%20my%20trip%20so%20I%20could%20maintain%20my%20nighttime%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20did%20light%20cardio%20workouts%20during%20long%20train%20stops.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20train%20stopped%20on%20the%20left%20with%20a%20station%20on%20the%20right%20and%20a%20mountan%20behind%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9a62b1fb3fcb42648f81d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20California%20Zephyr%20stops%20at%20some%20stations%20for%2010%20minutes%20or%20longer.%20In%20these%20cases%2C%20all%20passengers%20are%20allowed%20to%20step%20off%20the%20train.%20I%20got%20some%20fresh%20air%20at%20every%20long%20stop.%20I%20saw%20other%20travelers%20smoking%20tobacco%2C%20snapping%20pictures%2C%20and%20walking%20up%20and%20down%20the%20platform.%20But%20I%20was%20the%20only%20one%20doing%20jumping%20jacks%20and%20playing%20hopscotch%20with%20imaginary%20chalk%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20a%20bit%20like%20an%20outcast%2C%20but%20getting%20in%20some%20light%20cardio%20was%20worth%20feeling%20strange%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%20because%20I%20got%20to%20release%20pent-up%20energy%20and%20tire%20out%20my%20body%2C%20which%20probably%20helped%20me%20sleep%20better%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20made%20an%20effort%20to%20get%20to%20know%20fellow%20travelers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20table%20in%20front%20of%20a%20window%20in%20the%20dining%20car%20on%20the%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9a5881fb3fcb42648f803%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20to%20know%20people%20on%20a%20long-distance%20train%20makes%20me%20feel%20more%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20I%20run%20into%20the%20same%20people%20throughout%20the%20trip.%20While%20I%20often%20feel%20shy%20and%20awkward%20around%20strangers%2C%20I%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-solo-for-decade-best-tips-make-friends-stay-safe-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esolo%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20practice%20my%20social%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmtrak%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20talk%20to%20other%20passengers%20because%20they%20seat%20different%20parties%20together%20in%20the%20dining%20car.%20I%20learned%20about%20other%20people's%20travel%20plans%20over%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20many%20of%20my%20dining%20companions%20later%20on%20the%20platform%20during%20long%20stops%20and%20chatted%20with%20them%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20got%20off%20the%20train%2C%20I%20felt%20proud%20of%20myself%20for%20how%20much%20I'd%20grown%20as%20a%20train%20traveler.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20train%20stopped%20at%20a%20platform%20on%20the%20right%2C%20and%20people%20walk%20with%20suitcases%20on%20the%20left%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab1913d3e2f1aef36a249c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPassengers%20exit%20the%20train%20in%20Emeryville%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%2053-hour%20journey%20on%20the%20California%20Zephyr%