20Manya%20Jain%20of%20Knot%20Kisses%2C%20the%20journey%20to%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebegan%20in%20her%20bedroom%20during%20the%202020%20lockdown.%20She%20was%20barely%2013%20when%20she%20picked%20up%20a%20hook%20because%20she%20wanted%20new%20clothes%20and%20her%20mother%20refused%20to%20buy%20them.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20rebellion%20became%20a%20craft%2C%20and%20then%20a%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20taught%20myself%20entirely%20through%20YouTube%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandmother%20used%20to%20crochet%2C%20and%20I%20was%20always%20fascinated.%20With%20time%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leap%20from%20fashion%20accessories%20to%20wedding%20garlands%20came%20unexpectedly.%20At%20a%20Delhi%20event%20where%20she%20had%20set%20up%20a%20stall%2C%20a%20bride-to-be%20asked%20if%20she%20could%20make%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20her%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20moment%20was%20really%20special%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manya%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99d%20always%20imagined%20making%20one%20for%20my%20own%20wedding%20someday.%20To%20actually%20craft%20one%20for%20someone%20else%20felt%20surreal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDGk6a1syDvb%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDGk6a1syDvb%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20